# mainfactory

OpenComputers (Minecraft) TCP bridge in Go + MES prototype in Python on Postgres. Deployed to k3s.

- handlers/cmd/bot-handler, handlers/cmd/server-handler - separate Dockerfiles, shared handlers/internal/
- mes/migrations/ - Postgres SQL; apply with mes/scripts/migrate.py and DATABASE_URL
- mes/tests/lua/ - luasocket simulators for bots/servers (not Minecraft)
- deploy/k3s/ - postgres, bot-handler, server-handler

Keep changes minimal. No SQLite. See AGENTS.md and README.md for details.